        </section>
    </div>


    <main>
        <section class="container block py-5 "><!-- about us -->
            <div class="row">
                <article class="col-sm-5">
                    <h3>Use your feet to clean the street</h3>
                    <p>Take the trash you find to the litter box. Identify the trash cans in your town where you want to dump the trash you find en route.</p>
                </article>
                <article class="col-sm-2">
                    <img class="img-fluid" src="/assets/imgs/can.png"/>
                </article>
                <article class="col-sm-5">
                    <h3>Get those big trash producers moving too</h3>
                    <p>Without these lovely multinationals we wouldn't be able to plog. Let's thank them for their generous stream of trash by tagging them in our posts.</p>
                </article>
            </div>
        </section>
        
        <section class="container block pb-5" id="runs"><!-- challenges -->
            <section class="text-center mb-5">
                <h2>Challenge yourself</h2>
                <p class="lead lead-md">Choose different litter runs to keep your routes fresh and the streets clean</p>
            </section>

            <section class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                    <%- include('partials/card.ejs', {imgSrc: '/assets/imgs/run.jpg', cardTitle: 'Free Run', cardText: 'Enjoy your free run! Be inspired by the moment.'}) %>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                    <%- include('partials/card.ejs', {imgSrc: '/assets/imgs/bran.jpg', cardTitle: 'Brand', cardText: 'Had too much sugar? Use your energy to throw the coke cans away.'}) %>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                    <%- include('partials/card.ejs', {imgSrc: '/assets/imgs/park.jpg', cardTitle: 'Park', cardText: 'Tidy up our mucky parks and enjoy the fresh air.'}) %>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                    <%- include('partials/card.ejs', {imgSrc: '/assets/imgs/booze.jpg', cardTitle: 'Booze', cardText: 'Repent for all those drinks you had last night. Pick up beer cans.'}) %>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                    <%- include('partials/card.ejs', {imgSrc: '/assets/imgs/landmark.jpg', cardTitle: 'Landmarks', cardText: 'Become an major icon like our greatest landmarks.'}) %>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                    <%- include('partials/card.ejs', {imgSrc: '/assets/imgs/group.jpg', cardTitle: 'Group', cardText: 'Challenge your mateys, measure your loot, free run for the highest bidder! Savvy?'}) %>
                </div>
